milestones.description: Odumbe and Alpesh Vadher's 137-run partnership is KENYA's highest for the 6th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 42 between Odumbe and Tito Odumbe
Steve Tikolo has become the top scorer for KENYA in ODIs with 855 runs, going past Otieno's 843
Thomas Odoyo has become the top wicket-taker for KENYA in ODIs with 27 wickets, going past Aasif Karim's 24
Aasif Karim has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (30) for KENYA, going past Odumbe
